                                    <img class="bann_img" src="https://i.ibb.co/0nXvMM4/Untitled-design.png" alt="#" />
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <span>01/03</span>
                                    <h1>The Salon by Marian Libiran</h1>
                                    <p>Welcome to The Salon by Marian Libiran, where hair meets artistry. Our exclusive focus on hair services ensures that each client receives personalized attention and expertise.</p>
                                    <a class="get_btn" asp-action="Create" asp-controller="Appointment" role="button">Book Appointment</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <div class="container-fluid">
                        <div class="carousel-caption relative">
                            <div class="row d_flex">
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <img class="bann_img" src="https://i.ibb.co/2cT3Twb/the-salon.png" alt="#" />
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <span>02/03</span>
                                    <h1>Get #Marianized</h1>
                                    <p>
                                        At The Salon by Marian Libiran, we are committed to creating a welcoming and inclusive environment. We take pride in our attention to detail and personalized approach, ensuring that each client leaves feeling refreshed, rejuvenated, and absolutely stunning.

                                    </p>
                                    <a class="get_btn" asp-action="Create" asp-controller="Appointment" role="button">Book Appointment</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <div class="container-fluid">
                        <div class="carousel-caption relative">
                            <div class="row d_flex">
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <img class="bann_img" src="/images/banner3.png" alt="#" />
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <span>03/03</span>
                                    <h1>Organic Hair Treatments</h1>
                                    <p>
                                        At The Salon by Marian Libiran, we believe in the power of nature to reveal your hair’s natural beauty. Our expert stylists are here to guide you through a personalized treatment journey that will leave your hair looking and feeling its absolute best.
                                    </p>
                                    <a class="get_btn" asp-action="Create" asp-controller="Appointment" role="button">Book Appointment</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                    <i class="fa fa-long-arrow-left" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                </a>
                <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
                    <i class="fa fa-long-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
